SampleSizeTree - Class in org.gsusers.gsmv.model
Class SampleSizeTree The SampleSizeTree object contains the whole structure of the sample sizes for both crossed and nested facets, as well management of indices, incrementing indices (stepping), and calculation of of range for each configuration ('Effect').
